Package: review
Title: Tidy Relational Algebra for Semantic Review
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Language: en-GB
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Daniel", 
           family = "Antal", 
           email = "daniel.antal@dataobservatory.eu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7513-6760"))
Description: Provides a tidy framework for iterative semantic review of
    tabular data. The package extends tidy data workflows with review-aware
    data structures and operations that preserve candidate values, review
    history, provenance, reviewer attribution, and observation status while
    remaining compatible with ordinary tibbles. It is designed to support
    reproducible semantic stabilisation workflows and integrates naturally
    with the tidyverse and metadata packages such as 'dataset'.
